Package: emonhub
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-configobj, python-serial
Description: Interface with remote energy monitors and devices over RF
	Acts as an interface between devices such as emonTx that transmit
	data via RF or other means, and software that consumes this information
	such as MQTT or emoncms.
